title Detailed Sequence Diagram: Real-Time Bus Tracking Loop

' --- ACTORS & SYSTEMS ---
actor \"Driver\" as Driver
participant \"Driver PWA\n(Frontend)\" as D_App
participant \"Auth Service\n(Firebase)\" as Auth
database \"Realtime DB\n(Firebase)\" as DB
entity \"Google Maps\nAPI\" as Maps
participant \"Passenger PWA\n(Frontend)\" as P_App
actor \"Passenger\" as Pass

' --- 1. INITIALIZATION PHASE ---
group 1. Session Initialization
 Driver -> D_App : Click \"Start Trip\"
 activate D_App
 
 D_App -> Auth : Validate Session Token
 activate Auth
 Auth --> D_App : Token Valid (Role: DRIVER)
 deactivate Auth
 
 D_App -> D_App : Check GPS Hardware Status
 D_App -> DB : UPDATE /buses/{id} (Status=\"ACTIVE\")
 activate DB
 DB --> D_App : Write Success (Trip Started)
 deactivate DB
 
 D_App --> Driver : Show \"Tracking Active\" Dashboard
end

' --- 2. REAL-TIME TRACKING LOOP ---
group 2. Continuous Tracking Loop [Interval: 5s]
 ' A. CAPTURE & VALIDATE
 Driver -> D_App : Hardware GPS Signal (Lat, Lng)
 
 D_App -> D_App : Sanitize Data\n(Check for Null/Zero values)
 
 ' B. TRANSMISSION
 D_App -> DB : PUT /locations/{bus_id}\n{lat: 32.0, lng: 72.6, timestamp: t}
 activate DB
 DB --> D_App : HTTP 200 OK (Data Saved)
 
 ' C. SYNCHRONIZATION (Observer Pattern)
 ' Note: Firebase pushes data to listeners automatically
 DB -[#blue]> P_App : Event: onChildChanged(New Coords)
 deactivate DB
 activate P_App
 
 ' D. VISUALIZATION & CALCULATION
 P_App -> Maps : Request Map Update (Marker Position)
 activate Maps
 Maps --> P_App : Render Updated Tiles
 deactivate Maps
 
 P_App -> P_App : Recalculate Distance to User
 P_App -> P_App : Update Estimated Time (ETA)
 
 P_App -> Pass : Refresh Map UI (Move Bus Icon)
 deactivate P_App
end

' --- 3. TERMINATION PHASE ---
group 3. Trip Termination
 Driver -> D_App : Click \"Stop Trip\"
 D_App -> DB : UPDATE /buses/{id} (Status=\"IDLE\")
 activate DB
 DB --> D_App : Write Success
 deactivate DB
 
 DB -[#blue]> P_App : Event: Status Changed (IDLE)
 activate P_App
 P_App -> Pass : Remove Bus from Live Map
 deactivate P_App
 
 D_App --> Driver : Show Trip Summary
 deactivate D_App
end
